      "writtenOn": "2019-11-19T13:18:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Having some prose in a comment about the context in which the test data would originate helps me to review this w/o having to run the code. For example: \"this test case is an entry with many newly untriaged digests. There are 7 tests with untriaged digests and Gold isn\u0027t yet sure exactly which commit introduced them, so it\u0027s blaming them on Joe or Elisa.\"",
      "revId": "37704ea28ca3f3149d03a5193ee58e7ca701f435",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
